~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : bmail                                     ~FTRNUTS Version 3.0.2
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : bmail

   This command allows the admin to read the bots smail.  Future addition
   will be to enable the bot to send smail as well.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : cbot, qbot, bact
